Subject: [PATCH 24/28] SPEAr: add PCIE option in Kconfig

git://git.stlinux.com/spear/linux-2.6.git
commit 2367df7d ST SPEAr: Added PCIE host controller base driver support.

Adds suppport for Synopsys designware PCIE version 3.30a. Here add
PCIE option to select PCIE features for spear13xx.

Signed-off-by: Liming Wang <liming.wang@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/Kconfig |    1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/Kconfig b/arch/arm/Kconfig
index b2ad68f..d9fb576 100644
--- a/arch/arm/Kconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/Kconfig
@@ -1474,6 +1474,7 @@ config PCI_HOST_ITE8152
 	select DMABOUNCE
 
 source "drivers/pci/Kconfig"
+source "drivers/pci/pcie/Kconfig"
 
 source "drivers/pcmcia/Kconfig"
 
